Welcome to <%= @resource.team.name %>!

Hello <%= @resource.email %>,

You've been invited to join <%= @resource.team.name %> by <%= @resource.invited_by.email %>. Click the link below to accept the invitation and set up your account:

<%= accept_invitation_url(@resource, invitation_token: @token) %>

If the link doesn’t work, copy and paste the URL into your browser.

<% if @resource.invitation_due_at %>
This invitation will expire on <%= l(@resource.invitation_due_at, format: :'devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept_until_format') %>.
<% end %>

If you weren’t expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.